      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound BMW E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant equipped with individual throttle bodies and double VANOS. This example utilizes the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, delivering torque to the rear wheels through an M-Variable limited-slip differential. The chassis has been maintained with a focus on performance, including a reinforced rear subframe and refreshed suspension bushings to ensure structural rigidity. It exhibits a well-preserved exterior and interior consistent with a driver\u2019s car, prioritizing mechanical precision and linear throttle response over showroom-floor cosmetics. A perfect candidate for the enthusiast seeking a visceral, analog driving experience.",
